{"tid":667944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"太古城25歲女遭電話恐嚇 受驚報警","createTime":"2018-05-17T07:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T08:13:22.000Z","uid":47433,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"80a22a1e5cc1f621d6f237fded9780f6aa5faf1a","tid":667944,"uid":47433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T07:39:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180517/58202223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180517%2F58202223&d=mEyK4i52j5nGS%2BFZh4gAfp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=aba55b99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180517%2F58202223&h=a24991d7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180517/58202223</a><br />\n<br />\n凌晨2時50分，鰂魚涌太古城一名25歲女子報警，指被一名男子透過手提電話通訊程式言語恐嚇。警方接報到場調查，案件暫列作刑事恐嚇，交由東區警區刑事調查隊第五隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n係咪太古痴漢大將軍終於會俾人拉呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df7f4b84811189d2b2496a0688133f9160b0416","tid":667944,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:06:47.000Z","msg":"我都係第一時間諗到大將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a791de5dbbebf6f895057a7fd68da504402660c3","tid":667944,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T08:13:22.000Z","msg":"仲未坐監咩"}]}